==English==

===Etymology===
Apparently from the color [[beige]], coined by writer [[w:Mark Ames|Mark Ames]]

===Noun===
'''Beigeist'''

# A [[sellout]]; a [[conformist]] to [[bourgeois]] or corporate [[mediocracy]].

====Derived terms====
*[[beigeocracy]]

